[src:joi-validation/global-objects-object] The returned object has separate properties for each group, containing arrays with the elements in the group.
[src:joi-validation/global-objects-object] Returns `true` if the specified object has the indicated property as its *own* property, or `false` if the property is inherited or does not exist.
